hine learning. This work opens the door to\nfurther investigation of how automatically analysed respiratory patterns could\nbe used as pre-screening signals to aid COVID-19 diagnosis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2020 16:13:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Jul 2020 18:22:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 18 Jan 2021 07:08:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-19"}
