%) will eradicate\ninfections in the state of Texas within a year. Extending our fits for all of\nthe US states, we predict about 11 million total infections (including\nundetected), 8 million cumulative confirmed cases, and 630,000 cumulative\ndeaths by November 1, 2020.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2020 17:04:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 18 Jun 2020 22:56:43 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 Jun 2020 22:27:21 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2020 15:13:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-10"}
